name: 005:zūn šur (zoon shur - moon child)
description:
pa:dša:h sə:bnis de:va:n kha:nas, ti:l􏱁iv’ tsə:g’ daza:n chi.
s ə:ri: gatsha:n pa:nas pa:nas, kunuy zona: ro:za:n chu.

In the king’s palace; oil lamps are illuminated.
All will leave for their own places, only one person remains.
Moon child.

art & editing by zareen fava
 music by Kashmiri rabab player, Ali Shabir

50% will be donated to organizations supporting Kashmiris affected by occupation and the diaspora experience.
